 busy. Please try again in a few minutes.",errorForbidden:"Invalid or expired Figma connection. Please try reconnecting your Figma account.",errorNotFound:"Figma file not found. Please check the URL and make sure you have access to this file.",errorGeneric:"Unable to access this Figma design. Please check the URL and try again.",validating:"Checking...",switchAccount:"Switch Figma account",cancel:"Cancel",generate:"Generate",viewerCannotGenerate:"You have viewer access and cannot create apps. Contact your workspace admin to upgrade to Editor.",figmaFile:"Figma file",justNow:"Just now",importingMessage:"Generate an app based on your design from this Figma frame."},aO={connectFailed:"Failed to connect Figma. Please try again.",popupBlocked:"Popup blocked. Please allow popups and try again.",disconnected:"Figma disconnected",disconnectFailed:"Failed to disconnect Figma. Please try again."},nO={capturing:"Capturing...",figmaDescription:"Analyzing Figma design system. Extracting layout, typography, and color tokens to build your app."},iO={webApp:"Apps",aiAgent:"Superagents",recentApps:"Recent apps",templates:"Templates",favoritesComingSoon:"Favorites coming soon"},rO={new:"New",message:"Say hello to your real Personal Agent",cta:"Try it now"},oO=JSON.parse(`{"greeting":"Hi {{name}},","greetingGeneric":"Hi there,","title":"Build your own AI Personal Agent","createTitle":"Create your own Superagent","experimentCreateTitle":"Put your Superagent to work","newBadge":"New","subtitle":"Your AI agent that runs tasks, connects to your tools, and works for you 24/7","experimentSubtitle":"Describe a task, or start from an idea below","experimentInputPlaceholder":"Give your Superagent a task to do...","ideasLabel":"Or start from one of these ideas:","promptInput":{"addContextAriaLabel":"Add context","nextAriaLabel":"Next"},"ideas":{"categories":{"business":"Business","productivity":"Productivity","finance":"Finance","creative":"Creative","education":"Education","home":"Home","travel":"Travel"},"cards":{"findClients":{"title":"Find new clients while I sleep","description":"Every night, hunt for 10 new companies that fit my client profile, find the right contact, and draft an email I can send in the morning.","prompt":"Every night at 11pm, find 10 new companies that match my ideal client profile, identify the right person to contact at each on LinkedIn, and draft a personalized intro message for each one. Send it to me in the chat so I can review and send in the morning."},"trackCompetitors":{"title":"Track my competitors","description":"Every Monday morning, check 3 competitors' websites, pricing, TikTok and LinkedIn for changes, and send me a brief.","prompt":"Every Monday morning at 9am, check my main 3 competitors' websites, pricing pages, TikTok and LinkedIn for any changes since last week. Send me a short brief covering what shifted and why it matters for us."},"captureLeads":{"title":"Capture leads automatically","description":"Every morning, scan Gmail for new leads, log them in Google Sheets, and send intro replies.","prompt":"Every morning at 9am, scan my Gmail for new inbound leads, log each in a Google Sheet with name, company, email and source, and draft a personalized intro reply in my voice for me to approve and send."},"taxSeason":{"title":"Prepare me for tax season","description":"Every quarter, pull my income and expenses into a Google Sheet organized for my accountant.","prompt":"Every quarter, pull all transactions from Stripe and organize them into a Google Sheet with separate Income and Expenses tabs, categorized cleanly so I can hand it straight to my accountant."},"brandMentions":{"title":"Track brand mentions daily","description":"Every day, scan TikTok and the web for mentions of my company and summarize the sentiment.","prompt":"Every evening at 8pm, scan TikTok and the web for mentions of my brand. Send me a short summary covering total mentions, the overall sentiment breakdown, the top 3 most engaged posts, and anything that needs my response."},"revenueSummary":{"title":"Send me a weekly revenue summary","description":"Every Monday morning, pull last week's Stripe numbers vs the prior week and surface what changed.","prompt":"Every Monday at 9am, pull last week's Stripe numbers, revenue, new customers, MRR, churn, refunds, and compare each to the prior week. Highlight the biggest movers and explain what likely caused them."},"meetingBrief":{"title":"Prep me before every meeting","description":"30 min before every meeting, pull the invite, attendee info and recent emails into a short brief.","prompt":"30 minutes before any external meeting on my Google Calendar, send me a short brief with the meeting purpose, each attendee's role and company, the last few Gmail threads with anyone in the meeting, and 2–3 talking points."},"cleanInbox":{"title":"Clean my inbox daily","description":"Every morning, sort unread emails into reply today, FYI, and archive, and draft the urgent replies.","prompt":"Every morning at 8am, sort my unread Gmail into three buckets: Reply Today, FYI, and Archive, and draft replies in my voice for everything that needs a response so I just need to review and send."},"findNextRole":{"title":"Find my next role","description":"Search 5 senior roles posted this week, tailor my CV for each, and draft intro messages to hiring managers.","prompt":"Search for 5 senior roles posted in the last 7 days that match my background and preferences. For each role, tailor my CV to the job description and draft an intro message to the hiring manager."},"organizeDrive":{"title":"Organize my Drive every Sunday","description":"Every Sunday, scan my Google Drive for unsorted files and move them into the right folders automatically.","prompt":"Every Sunday evening at 8pm, scan my Google Drive for new and unsorted files from the past week and move them into the right folders based on filename, content and existing structure. Flag anything ambiguous instead of guessing."},"planDay":{"title":"Plan my day each morning","description":"Every morning, review my calendar and tasks, and tell me the 3 priorities for today.","prompt":"Every weekday at 8am, review today's Google Calendar and my open Notion tasks, then send me a message with my top 3 priorities for the day, the focus time I have between meetings, and any scheduling conflicts."},"stuckPrs":{"title":"Follow up on stuck PRs","description":"When a PR I own sits unreviewed for 4+ hours, send the reviewer a polite Slack nudge.","prompt":"Monitor my open GitHub PRs. When a PR I've authored sits without review activity for 4+ hours during work hours, send the assigned reviewer a polite Slack DM with the PR link and a one-line summary of what changed."},"stockMoves":{"title":"Catch big stock moves","description":"When any stock on my watchlist moves 5%+ in a day, ping me on Telegram or WhatsApp with the reason.","prompt":"When any stock on my watchlist moves 5% or more in a day vs the previous close, send me a Telegram or WhatsApp message with the ticker, % change, current price, and the most likely reason based on news from the last 24 hours."},"stocksWatching":{"title":"Suggest stocks worth watching","description":"Every Monday, surface 5 stocks worth a closer look based on my interests, risk profile, and what's moving in the market.","prompt":"Every Monday morning, surface 5 stocks worth a closer look this week, based on my interests, risk profile and what's moving in the market. For each: ticker, why now, key risk, and a brief valuation snapshot. Don't repeat picks from the last 4 weeks."},"unusedSubscriptions":{"title":"Find subscriptions I don't use","description":"Scan Gmail for every subscription, calculate the monthly total, flag duplicates, and suggest what to cut.","prompt":"Scan my Gmail from the past year for recurring charges and renewal notices. Build a list of every active subscription with its monthly cost, calculate my total monthly spend, flag duplicates or overlapping services, and suggest the top 3 to cancel and why."},"monthlyFinanceCheck":{"title":"Check in with me monthly on finances","description":"First of every month, review my income, spending, investments, and surface one thing to improve.","prompt":"On the 1st of every month, review last month's income, spending and investments in my finance Google Sheet vs the previous 3-month average. Send me a short summary with the biggest movers and one specific, actionable thing to improve next month."},"earningsSeason":{"title":"Track earnings season","description":"When a company I own reports earnings, log the results, guidance, and analyst reaction in a Google Sheet.","prompt":"When a company I own reports earnings, within 24 hours log into a Google Sheet: date, EPS actual vs estimate, revenue actual vs estimate, forward guidance, key analyst takes, and stock reaction. Send me a quick summary too."},"savingsGoal":{"title":"Plan a big savings goal","description":"I want to save $20k in 18 months. Build a monthly plan and check in with me every month.","prompt":"I want to save $20,000 in 18 months. Build a monthly savings plan in a Google Sheet showing target balance and required contribution per month. On the 1st of every month, compare actual vs plan, send me a status update, and adjust the remaining months if I'm ahead or behind."},"dailyContentIdea":{"title":"Daily content idea","description":"Every morning at 8am, send me one fresh content idea based on what's trending and what I've already made.","prompt":"Every morning at 8am, send me one content idea for today based on what's trending in my niche on TikTok and LinkedIn, what my audience engages with most, and what I haven't already posted recently. Include the hook, a quick outline, and which platform fits best."},"viralOpportunities":{"title":"Spot viral opportunities","description":"Monitor TikTok trends daily and ping me on Telegram when something in my niche starts blowing up.","prompt":"Monitor TikTok daily for trending sounds, formats and topics in my niche. The moment something starts gaining real momentum and fits my style, send me a Telegram message with an example post, why it's working, and a quick angle I could use."},"topicContentPlan":{"title":"Research a topic and plan content","description":"Research a topic deeply and turn it into a 5-part series with scripts, hooks, and posting order in Google Docs.","prompt":"Research a topic I give you deeply — credible sources, real examples, recent discussions — then turn it into a 5-part content series in a Google Doc with a series arc, per-post hooks, full scripts, posting order, and a recommended cadence."},"weeklyPerformanceReview":{"title":"Weekly performance review","description":"Every Monday, review last week's TikTok numbers, surface what worked, and suggest what to do more of.","prompt":"Every Monday morning, log last week's TikTok posts into a Google Sheet with views, likes, shares, saves and completion rate. Send me a summary with my top performers, common patterns in what worked, what flopped and why, and 3 specific ideas to test this week."},"newsletterFromContent":{"title":"Newsletter draft from my content","description":"Every Friday, pull my week's posts from TikTok and draft a newsletter I can send to my list.","prompt":"Every Friday afternoon, pull this week's TikTok posts and draft a newsletter in a Google Doc — short personal intro in my voice, 3–5 highlights with embedded links and added context, and a closing thought or question for readers."},"audienceResearch":{"title":"Research my audience","description":"Analyze my followers and top-performing posts and tell me who my actual audience is and what they want.","prompt":"Analyze my TikTok followers and my top 20 posts from the last 90 days. Tell me who my actual audience is, what topics and formats consistently outperform, what comments and DMs reveal about what they want more of, and 3 content directions worth leaning into."},"lecturesToNotes":{"title":"Turn lectures into notes","description":"Send a voice note or video and get a clean summary saved to Notion or Google Doc for review later.","prompt":"When I send you a voice note, video or lecture recording, transcribe it and produce clean structured notes: a one-paragraph summary, key concepts as bullets, definitions of new terms, and 3–5 review questions. Save it to Notion or a Google Doc, titled with date and topic."},"examPrep":{"title":"Prepare me for an exam","description":"Build a 6-week study plan, send daily drills at 10am, and run a quiz every evening at 7pm.","prompt":"Build a 6-week study plan in Notion for the exam I'm preparing for, broken into weekly themes and daily topics. Every day at 10am, send me 3 practice problems on the day's topic. Every evening at 7pm, quiz me with 5 questions covering today plus spaced repetition. Track my scores in a Google Sheet."},"personalTeacher":{"title":"Be my personal teacher","description":"Every morning at 8am, send a new lesson on my chosen skill, assign daily practice, and test me every week.","prompt":"Teach me a skill I choose. Every morning at 8am, send today's lesson with a concept, an example, and one practice exercise. Every Sunday evening, test me with 10 questions covering the week's lessons and adjust the difficulty based on how I score."},"flashcardsFromNotes":{"title":"Build flashcards from my notes","description":"Turn my Notion notes into flashcard drills and every evening send me 5 questions on iMessage.","prompt":"Turn my Notion notes into flashcards (question on one side, answer on the other). Every evening, send me 5 questions on iMessage, prioritizing cards I've gotten wrong before and ones I haven't seen in a while. Track my answers over time."},"secondBrain":{"title":"Build my second brain","description":"Every day, pull ideas from my chats, notes, and readings, and organize them into a growing Notion knowledge base.","prompt":"Every day, pull interesting ideas, quotes and concepts from my recent chats with you, notes and readings I share. Organize them into my Notion knowledge base under the right topics, link related notes together, and flag any concept I've revisited 3+ times as important."},"learningReview":{"title":"Weekly learning review","description":"Every Sunday, review what I learned this week across my notes and chats, and summarize it in a Google Doc.","prompt":"Every Sunday evening, review everything I added this week across my Notion notes and our chats. Summarize it in a Google Doc: my top 5 ideas, key questions I'm still wrestling with, and connections between this week's topics and previous weeks."},"renovationPlan":{"title":"Plan a renovation end to end","description":"Research contractors, compare quotes, track expenses against budget, and keep the full project in Google Sheets.","prompt":"Help me plan my renovation end to end. Research and compare contractors, log every quote, track expenses against my budget by category, and maintain a timeline with milestones — all in a Google Sheet. Update weekly and flag when I'm trending over budget."},"familySchedules":{"title":"Coordinate family schedules","description":"Every Sunday night, pull everyone's week into one shared calendar and flag the conflicts.","prompt":"Every Sunday at 8pm, pull each family member's calendar for the upcoming week into our shared Google Calendar. Send me a summary flagging conflicts, overlapping commitments, pickup gaps, and double-booked drivers."},"schoolUpdates":{"title":"Stay on top of school updates","description":"When my kid's school sends an email, extract events and deadlines into my calendar and summarize what I need to do.","prompt":"When my kid's school sends an email, extract any events, deadlines, permission slips and supplies needed. Add the events to Google Calendar with reminders, and send me a summary of what I need to do, by when, and what to buy or sign."},"wishlistPriceDrops":{"title":"Spot price drops on my wishlist","description":"Watch prices on items I'm waiting to buy and alert me on iMessage or Telegram when any of them drops.","prompt":"Track the prices of items on my wishlist daily. When any item drops 10% or more vs the last 7 days, or hits a target price I've set, send me an iMessage or Telegram with the item, current price, previous price, % drop and a direct link to buy."},"billsReminder":{"title":"Never miss a bill","description":"Scan Gmail for incoming bills, log the due date in Google Sheets, and remind me 3 days before each one.","prompt":"Scan my Gmail for incoming bills and log each one in a Google Sheet with vendor, amount, due date, autopay status and category. 3 days before each due date, remind me with the amount and a payment link if available."},"movingPlan":{"title":"Plan my move to a new home","description":"Find movers, compare quotes, build a packing checklist, and schedule every milestone.","prompt":"Help me plan my move. Research 5 moving companies and compare quotes in a Google Sheet, build a packing checklist by room, and schedule every milestone in my Google Calendar — booking movers, transferring utilities, change of address, packing deadlines, move day. Remind me 3 days before each."},"flightPriceDrops":{"title":"Notify when flight prices drop","description":"Twice a day, check flights to a destination I choose and alert me when prices drop or a deal appears.","prompt":"Twice a day, check flights to a destination I choose for the dates I give you. Alert me when prices drop 10%+ vs the last 7 days, or when a real deal appears below my target. Send airline, dates, price and a direct booking link."},"nextTrip":{"title":"Find my next trip","description":"Based on my budget, dates, and vibe, research 5 destinations, compare flights and hotels, and recommend the best one.","prompt":"Based on the budget, dates, vibe and origin city I give you, research 5 destinations matching the vibe, compare flights and hotels for each in a Google Sheet, and recommend your top pick with clear reasoning."},"entireTrip":{"title":"Organize my entire trip","description":"Research flights and hotels, suggest restaurants and activities, and build a full itinerary in my calendar.","prompt":"For my upcoming trip, research and recommend flights and a hotel within budget, suggest restaurants and activities matching my interests, then build a day-by-day itinerary in Notion and add events to Google Calendar with addresses and reservation details."},"travelExpenses":{"title":"Track my travel spending","description":"Every trip, log every expense email into a Google Sheet so I know the true total when I get home.","prompt":"When I tell you a trip is starting, monitor Gmail for receipts, booking confirmations and expense emails for those dates. Log each into a Google Sheet by category — flights, hotel, food, activities, transport. At trip end, send me total spend by category vs my budget."},"tripResearchBrief":{"title":"Research before a trip","description":"Deliver a brief covering recommendations, local customs, weather, tipping, safety, visa rules, and what to avoid.","prompt":"For my upcoming trip, build a Google Doc brief covering visa requirements, weather forecast, local customs and etiquette, tipping norms, safety tips and areas to avoid, public transport basics, common scams, and 5 unmissable things to do. Keep it skimmable."},"saveMoneyTrip":{"title":"Save money on my trip","description":"Analyze my planned trip and find cheaper flights, hotel alternatives, free activities, and local deals.","prompt":"Look at my planned trip in Notion and find ways to cut total cost — cheaper flights with similar timing, hotel alternatives in the same area, free or low-cost activities replacing paid ones, public transit instead of taxis, and current local deals or city passes. Show savings as a clear before/after total."}}},"cta":"Create your Superagent","creating":"Creating...","continueHero":{"heading":"Pick up where you left off","continueBtn":"Continue with {{name}}","or":"Or","createNew":"Create a new superagent","activeAgo":"Active {{time}}","you":"You"},"features":{"hassleFree":{"title":"Hassle free","desc":"No Docker, no servers, no setup. Just run your Superagent."},"alwaysOn":{"title":"Always on","desc":"Runs tasks and automations for you, 24/7."},"actions":{"title":"Takes real action","desc":"Handles tasks, sends updates, and reacts automatically."},"remembers":{"title":"Remembers everything","desc":"Keeps track of your goals, preferences, and context."},"everywhere":{"title":"Lives where you are","desc":"Works in WhatsApp, Telegram, Slack, and your browser."},"secure":{"title":"Secure by default","desc":"Access only to what you allow."}},"untitled":"Untitled Agent","active":"Active","noDescription":"No description available","edited":"Edited {{time}}","updated":"Updated {{time}}","failedToCreate":"Failed to create agent. Please try again.","errorPage":{"title":"Oops, something went wrong","descriptionLine1":"There was a technical issue on our side.","descriptionLine2":"Go back to the agent creation page and try again","goToAgents":"Go to Agents →"}}`),sO={edited:"Edited {{time}}",updated:"Updated {{time}}",updatedRecently:"Updated recently"},lO={emptyTitle:"You haven't created any apps yet.",emptySubtitle:"Create your first app using the form above!"},cO={dialogTitle:"Quick navigation",dialogDescription:"Jump to apps, templates, billing, and workspace settings from the homepage.",searchPlaceholder:"Search apps, settings, templates, billing...",searching:"Searching workspace apps...",emptyTitle:"No matching destination",emptyDescription:"Try an app name, a settings section, or a page like billing or templates.",allApps:"All apps",backToWorkspace:"Back to workspace",templates:"Templates",billing:"Billing",groups:{apps:"Apps",navigate:"Pages",workspace:"Workspace",account:"Account"},subtitles:{favoriteApp:"Favorite app",recentApp:"Recent app",page:"Page"}},dO={label:"What would you like to create?",more:"More",moreIdeas:"More ideas",categories:{CRM:"CRM","Dev productivity":"Dev Productivity",Educational:"Educational","Content Generation and Editing":"Content Generation and Editing","Personal Finance":"Personal Finance","Health and Wellness":"Health and Wellness",Productivity:"Productivity","Travel Planning":"Travel Planning",Entertainment:"Entertainment",Environmental:"Environmental","Home Management":"Home Management","Creative Tools":"Creative Tools",Tasks:"Tasks","CRM & Sales":"CRM & Sales",Portfolio:"Portfolio",Finance:"Finance","Scheduling & Booking":"Scheduling & Booking",eCommerce:"eCommerce","Construction & Trade":"Construction & Trade","Events & Community":"Events & Community",Wellness:"Wellness","Operations & Logistics":"Operations & Logistics","Tasks & Workflows":"Tasks & Workflows","Content & Sites":"Content & Sites",Booking:"Booking","E-commerce":"E-Commerce",Projects:"Projects",Operations:"Operations"}},uO={hero:UL,recentApps:qL,recentAgents:VL,chat:$L,catalog:WL,billing:GL,permissions:HL,validation:YL,urlCapture:KL,integrations:ZL,connectors:JL,planMode:QL,viewAll:XL,error:eO,figmaDialog:tO,figmaOAuth:aO,statusBanner:nO,tabs:iO,tryAgentBanner:rO,agent:oO,appCard:sO,appsList:lO,commandPalette:cO,ideas:dO},pO={title:"Integrations",subtitle:"Discover pre-built integrations that let you connect to APIs, services, and tools to extend your app's capabilities."},mO={placeholder:"Search integrations..."},gO={title:"No matching integrations found",description:"Try adjusting your search or filter settings."},hO={title:"Connectors",subtitle:"Quick OAuth connections to popular services, supported by Base44."},fO={howToUse:"How to use",dialog:{getStarted:"Get started",navigateInstruction:"Navigate to your app's Integrations tab to connect {{name}} and get personalized prompts.",upgradeNotice:"This integration requires backend functions, a feature available only on Builder tier and above. <seePlansLink>See Plans</seePlansLink>"}},vO={stripe:"Sell products or subscriptions and get paid online.",salesforce:"Automate and sync CRM records.",slack:"Send messages and manage Slack as a user.",slackbot:"Post as a branded bot in your Slack workspace.",notion:"Organize and sync knowledge or project data.",googlecalendar:"Manage your schedule and calendar events.",googledrive:"Export and back up app-generated files.",gmail:"Automate email sending and inbox management.",googlesheets:"Sync and manage spreadsheet data.",googleslides:"Generate and manage presentations.",googledocs:"Manage and automate document creation.",googlebigquery:"Query and sync analytics data.",googletasks:"Manage to-do lists and tasks.",googlemeet:"Video conferences and meetings.",hubspot:"Sync CRM data and automate marketing.",linkedin:"Share updates and access professional profiles.",tiktok:"Track your profile stats and browse your videos.",discord:"Notify channels and integrate with your Discord community.",wix:"Access Wix site data and business tools.",github:"Manage repos, issues, and pull requests.",gitlab:"Manage projects, MRs, and CI/CD pipelines.",bamboohr:"Employee directory and HR management.",wrike:"Project planning and team coordination.",box:"Secure cloud content management.",clickup:"Organize projects and track team work.",google_analytics:"Track website traffic and user insights.",outlook:"Email and calendar.",linear:"Issue tracking and project management.",dropbox:"Store and sync files in the cloud.",google_search_console:"SEO and search analytics.",google_classroom:"Education and course management.",airtable:"Flexible databases and spreadsheets.",splitwise:"Expense splitting and group bills.",microsoft_teams:"Team chat, channels, and meetings.",share_point:"Document management and collaboration.",one_drive:"Cloud file storage.",typeform:"Forms, surveys, and data collection.",hugging_face:"AI inference and model repos.",calendly:"Automated appointment scheduling.",contentful:"Headless CMS and content management.",supabase:"Browse schemas, read data, and view project status (read-only)."},bO={page:pO,search:mO,emptyState:gO,connectors:hO,connector:fO,catalog:vO},yO={title:"Launchpad",subtitle:"Showcase your app to millions of makers and users.<br/>The most upvoted apps win credits every week.",launchMyApp:"Launch my app!",allApps:"All Apps",noAppsFound:"No apps found",noAppsHint:"Try clearing your filters or searching for something else.",noAppsEmpty:"Be the first to publish an app on Launchpad!",clearFilters:"Clear filters",goToFirstPage:"Go to first page",retry:"Retry",publishedToast:"Your app is now live on Launchpad!"},kO={votingStartsIn:"Voting starts in {{countdown}}",votingStartsSoon:"Voting starts soon",headline:"Give your app its launch moment",description:"Submit your published app to Base44's weekly showcase, where the community can discover it, vote for it, and help it reach new users.",submitCta:"Submit your app",learnMore:"Learn more",howItWorks:"How it works",steps:{submit:{title:"Submit your app",body:"Pick a public, published app, then add the details that help people discover and try it."},vote:{title:"Collect votes",body:"Voting opens every Monday. Share your launch with your community to climb the leaderboard."},win:{title:"Win credits & spotlight",body:"Top 3 makers earn free credits and a featured spot on the launchpad."}}},wO={placeholder:"Search apps on Launchpad..."},AO={all:"All"},SO={title:"Trending Now",empty:"No trending apps for this period yet.",period:{week:"7d",month:"30d",allTime:"All time"}},CO={live:"Live",someone:"Someone",sentences:{vote:"{{user}} just voted on {{app}}",like:"{{user}} just liked {{app}}",publish:"{{user}} just published {{app}}",default:"{{user}} just interacted with {{app}}"}},DO={signInPrompt:"Please sign in to publish your app on Launchpad.",signIn:"Sign in",back:"Back",next:"Next",publish:"Publish",publishing:"Publishing...",stepOf:"Step {{current}} of {{total}}",successToast:"Your app is now live on Launchpad!",failedDefault:"Failed to publish. Please try again.",categoriesLoadFailed:"Failed to load categories. Please close and try again.",categoriesRetry:"Retry",steps:{selectApp:"Select App",details:"Details",preview:"Preview"},appPicker:{chooseApp:"Choose which app you'd like to publish on Launchpad.",searchPlaceholder:"Search your apps...",loadFailed:"Failed to load your apps.",tryAgain:"Try again",noApps:"You don't have any apps yet.",noAppsForQuery:'No apps found for "{{query}}"',loadMore:"Load more",viewGrid:"Grid view",viewList:"List view"},preview:{caption:"Here's how your app will appear in the Launchpad grid:",creatorFallback:"You"},categoryPicker:{count:"{{current}}/{{max}} categories selected"},validation:{nameRequired:"App name is required",descriptionRequired:"Short description is required",descriptionTooLong:"Max {{max}} characters",categoriesRequired:"Select at least 1 category",screenshotsRequired:"Upload at least 1 screenshot"}},TO={selectApp:{title:"Select the app you'd like to submit",subtitle:"Only public and published apps can be submitted.",searchPlaceholder:"Search your apps...",noAppsFound:"No apps match your search.",noAppsAvailable:"You don't have any public, published apps yet.",loadMore:"Load more apps",loading:"Loading…",editedAgo:"Edited {{timeAgo}}",editedRecently:"Edited recently",continue:"Continue"},header:{breadcrumbLaunchpad:"Launchpad",breadcrumbCurrent:"Submit your app",title:"Submit your app",cancel:"Cancel",preview:"Preview",previewComingSoon:"Preview is coming soon.",submit:"Submit",submitting:"Submitting…"},successDialog:{title:"Your app is submitted to Launchpad!",body:"{{appName}} is ready for the next voting round. Once voting opens, people can discover it, try it, and vote.",done:"Done"},errors:{alreadySubmitted:"You've already submitted this app.",slugConflict:"A listing with this name already exists. Try a different name.",generic:"Couldn't submit. Please try again."},selectedApp:{title:"Selected app",subtitle:"This is the public app you're submitting to Launchpad.",selectAnother:"Select another app",viewLiveApp:"View live app",manageApp:"Manage app",editLogo:"Edit app logo",renameApp:"Rename app",appSettings:"Go to app settings"},launchDetails:{title:"Launch details",subtitle:"Add the details that help people understand what you built and why they should try it.",categories:"Categories",tagline:"Tagline",taglineTooltip:"Shown beside your app name in the Launchpad grid. Aim for one clear sentence under {{max}} characters.",taglinePlaceholder:"A one-line summary of what your app does.",description:"Description",descriptionPlaceholder:"Tell people more about your app...",improveWithAi:"Improve with AI",improveFailed:"Couldn't improve description. Please try again.",previewCard:"Preview your Launchpad card"},showcase:{title:"Showcase your app",subtitle:"Add up to 5 screenshots to help people understand your app before they open it."}},EO={uploadFailed:"Some screenshots failed to upload. Please try again.",uploading:"Uploading...",addImage:"Add image",count:"{{current}}/{{max}} screenshots. Drag to reorder.",autoCapturing:"Capturing your app..."},PO={previous:"Previous",next:"Next",pageOf:"Page {{page}} of {{totalPages}}"},xO={justNow:"just now",minutesAgo:"{{count}}m ago",hoursAgo:"{{count}}h ago",daysAgo:"{{count}}d ago"},_O={appName:"App Name",shortDescription:"Short Description",shortDescriptionPlaceholder:"A brief description of what your app does",shortDescriptionGenerating:"Generating with AI...",shortDescriptionGenerateFailed:"Couldn't generate description. Please try again.",longDescription:"Long Description",longDescriptionPlaceholder:"Tell people more about your app...",optional:"Optional",categories:"Categories",screenshots:"Screenshots",generateWithAi:"Generate with AI",aiComingSoon:"AI generation coming soon"},IO={tryApp:"Try App",share:"Share",shareToast:"Link copied to clipboard!",shareError:"Failed to share",about:"About",moreByCreator:"More by {{name}}",backToLaunchpad:"Back to Launchpad",notFound:"App not found",notFoundHint:"This app may have been removed or unpublished.",loadFailed:"Failed to load app details.",unknownCreator:"this creator"},zO={title:"Comments",placeholder:"Write a comment...",submit:"Post",submitting:"Posting...",empty:"No comments yet. Be the first!",loadMore:"Load more comments",deleteFailed:"Failed to delete comment.",postFailed:"Failed to post comment.",signInToComment:"Sign in to leave a comment",anonymous:"Anonymous"},RO={likeFailed:"Failed to update like.",voteFailed:"Failed to update vote.",selfVoteError:"You cannot vote for your own app."},MO={loadFailed:"Failed to load Launchpad data. Please try again.",browseFailed:"Failed to load apps. Please try again.",categoriesFailed:"Failed to load categories.",refreshFailed:"Failed to refresh — please reload the page."},NO={page:yO,comingSoon:kO,search:wO,categories:AO,trending:SO,liveActivity:CO,publish:DO,submit:TO,screenshots:EO,pagination:PO,relativeTime:xO,fillDetails:_O,detail:IO,comments:zO,engagement:RO,errors:MO},FO={title:"Apps",allAgentsTitle:"All Agents",createNewApp:"Create New App",createNewAgent:"Create New Agent",tabRecents:"Recents",tabFavorites:"Favorites",tabAllApps:"All Apps",tabAllAgents:"All Agents",searchPlaceholder:"Search apps",gridView:"Grid view",listView:"List view",appTypeLabel:"App type",appTypeApps:"Apps",appTypeAgents:"Agents",tableHeaderName:"Name",tableHeaderDescription:"Description",tableHeaderActions:"Actions",folderActionAddApps:"Add Apps",folderActionRename:"Rename",folderActionDelete:"Delete",filterOwnedByMe:"Owned by me",filterMyAppsPersonal:"My apps (personal workspace)",filterAllPlatform:"All apps (platform wide)",filterMyAppsWorkspace:"My apps in {{workspaceName}} workspace",filterAllAppsWorkspace:"All apps in {{workspaceName}} workspace",addNewFolder:"Add New Folder",sortLastUpdated:"Last updated",sortLastCreated:"Last created",sortNameAsc:"Name (A-Z)",sortNameDesc:"Name (Z-A)",filterCreatedByMe:"Created by me",filterCreatedByAnyone:"Created by anyone",filterAllPlatformApps:"All p